				\begin{document}$${u}_{i}={s}_{min}+\frac{{x}_{i}-\,\min ({x}_{i})}{\max ({x}_{i})-\,\min ({x}_{i})}({s}_{max}-{s}_{min})$$\end{document}ui=smin+xi−min(xi)max(xi)−min(xi)(smax−smin)where xi is the original value of the proxy variable i, ui is the standardized value of xi, max(xi) is the maximum value of the proxy variable i, min(xi) is the minimum value of the proxy variable i, smax is the standardized maximum value of 1, and smin is the standardized minimum value of 100.

